{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "b2c3d4e5-f6a7-8901-bcde-f12345678901",
    "name": "Smart Licitaciones — Auth (auto tokens)",
    "description": "Los tokens se guardan solos en el entorno tras cada respuesta.\n\n**Requisito:** `MAIL_HOST` vacío y `NODE_ENV=development` → la API devuelve `devActivationToken` y `devResetToken`.\n\n**Flujo rápido:** carpeta **▶ RUN — Flujo automático** → Collection Runner → Run.\n\n**Variables que se actualizan solas:** `activationToken`, `resetToken`, `preAuthToken`, `accessToken`, `targetUserId`.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "event": [
    {
      "listen": "test",
      "script": {
        "type": "text/javascript",
        "exec": [
          "try {",
          "  const body = pm.response.json();",
          "  if (body.devActivationToken) {",
          "    pm.environment.set('activationToken', body.devActivationToken);",
          "    console.log('✓ activationToken guardado');",
          "  }",
          "  if (body.devResetToken) {",
          "    pm.environment.set('resetToken', body.devResetToken);",
          "    console.log('✓ resetToken guardado');",
          "  }",
          "  if (body.usuario?.id) {",
          "    pm.environment.set('targetUserId', String(body.usuario.id));",
          "    console.log('✓ targetUserId = ' + body.usuario.id);",
          "  }",
          "  if (body.preAuthToken) {",
          "    pm.environment.set('preAuthToken', body.preAuthToken);",
          "    console.log('✓ preAuthToken guardado');",
          "  }",
          "  if (body.accessToken) {",
          "    pm.environment.set('accessToken', body.accessToken);",
          "    console.log('✓ accessToken guardado');",
          "  }",
          "} catch (e) {",
          "  // respuesta no JSON",
          "}"
        ]
      }
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "▶ RUN — Flujo automático (ejecutar en orden)",
      "description": "Postman → Collection Runner → selecciona solo esta carpeta → Run.\nTodos los tokens se guardan solos.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "1. GET Health",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
